description:
NLB Klik je usluga NLB Banke za brzo, jednostavno i bezbjedno mobilno bankarstvo.
Mobilno bankarstvo NLB Klik Crna Gora ME
Mobilno bankarstvo NLB Klik Crna Gora ME omogućava jednostavno i sigurno obavljanje bankarskih usluga putem mobilnog telefona.
Prednosti NLB Klik-a:
- Omogućava jednostavno i sigurno upravljanje finansijama, bilo kada i bilo gdje;
- Funkcioniše u mobilnim mrežama svih mobilnih operatera;

NLB Klik is a service of NLB Bank for fast, simple and secure mobile banking. 
Mobile banking NLB Klik Crna Gora ME
NLB Klik Crna Gora ME mobile banking enables simple and secure banking services via mobile phone.
Advantages of NLB Klik:
- Enables simple and secure financial management, anytime and anywhere;
- Functions in mobile networks of all mobile operators;
- Replaces the Internet banking service of NLB Bank in situations when you do not have a computer with you;

Upravljaj svojim finansijama sigurno i efikasno, gdje god da se nalaziš!

Prednosti Prva m-bank servisa:
jednostavan za korišćenje - moderan i funkcionalan dizajn;
uvijek dostupan - u svakom trenutku imaš uvid u svoje račune i možeš vršiti transakcije;
štedi vrijeme - brzo realizovanje plaćanja, bez posjete filijalama.

Prva m-bank ti omogućava:
uvid u stanje i promet po računima (tekući, devizni, računi štednje), platnim karticama i kreditima;
prenos sredstava sa jednog računa na drugi, izmirivanje obaveza po kreditnim karticama i kreditima;
plaćanje i prebacivanje novca na račune svih banaka u zemlji;
mjenjačnicu - prenos sredstava uz konverziju valuta;
kreditni kalkulator i kalkulator štednje;
pregled kursne liste.

Aktiviranje servisa je jednostavno - popuni pristupnicu na našem web sajtu ili u najbližoj filijali i nakon potpisivanja ugovora moći ćeš da uživaš u svim prednostima mobilnog bankarstva. Više informacija pronađi na našem veb-sajtu www.prvabankacg.com ili pozovi Kontakt centar na broj 19891. 


Manage your finances safely and efficiently, wherever you are!

Benefits of the Prva m-bank service:
• easy to use - modern and functional design;
• always available - you can view your accounts and make transactions at any time;
• saves time - quick payment, without visiting branches.

Prva m-bank allows you:
• insight into the balance and turnover of accounts (current, foreign currency, savings accounts), payment cards and loans;
• transferring funds from one account to another, settling credit card and loan obligations;
• paying and transferring money to the accounts of all banks in the country;
• exchange office - transfer of funds with currency conversion;
• loan calculator and savings calculator;
• review of the exchange rate list.

Activation of the service is simple - fill in the application form on our website or at your nearest branch, and after signing the contract you will be able to enjoy all the benefits of mobile banking. Find more information on our website www.prvabankacg.com or contact our Call Center at 19891.
